      "widgets_values": [
        "# 🎬 AUTO MOVIE DIRECTOR\n\n## 1 — WRITE: type your movie idea in the Planner. Set scenes & seconds.\n\n## 2 — PREVIEW: mode = `1) storyboard preview` → press Queue. Storyboard appears on the Renderer + saved to `output/auto_movie/`.\n\n## 3 — APPROVE: happy? Touch nothing. Not happy? Edit idea/overrides, Queue again.\n\n## 4 — RENDER: flip mode to `2) full movie` → Queue. Scenes start from your approved frames, get motion + sound, stitched into one MP4.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
